steps.description:
* Walk to Hammerfall
* Skip First Quest at the Entrance,
* Accept "HAMMERFALL" 
* Turn in "HAMMERFALL" accept next Part "Rising Spirit"
* go the Stairs up, get Flight point
* Leave hammerfall, Kill Raptors (Loot item)
* Go Back turn in quest and (Again, and agian)
* Skip Guile of the Raptor (for now)
* Port back To Ogrimmar (Hearthstone!)
steps.tips:
* This is a 7-8minute run
* Be careful elite (38) on the street.

steps.description:
* Kill as many Drywhisker in front of the cave as possible (not many inside)
* Go in the "Hidden Cave", Loot Items from Mobs
* go if have 12 Mote of Myzrael, to the little Monolith in the Cave, Turn in, Accept Next part
* Leave the Cave
* Go to Hammerfall

* in OG put the Rod of Helcular on the bank.
* Sell items, Resupply
* go to the zeppelin 
* Fly to Stranglethorn (NORTH ZEPPELIN Spot)
steps.tips:
* Abort all Hillsbrand Quests, with exception of, Elixir of Argony and Helcular's Revenge
* You should have now around ~4 quests (class quests not counting)

steps.description:
* Get in Grom'Gol the Flight point, Leave all Quest
* Go north to the Camp 
* Accept "Welcome to the Junge" / Turn in Quest
* Accept All Quests (Skip "Green Hills of StV.")

* Kill First all 10 Tiger Around the Camp
* Move north over the Bridge, Kill 10 Panther
* if done, Go Back Turn in Quests / accept next parts
steps.tips: if you need some extra Tiger / Panther (BLUE)

steps.description:
* Kill all needed Panther / Tiger / Raptors
* Go back to Camp
* Turn in Quests, DON'T ACCPET NEXT PARTS (SKIP, for now)
* Accept only next Parts for Tiger AND Raptors!!!
* Hearthstone to Orgrimmar!
steps.tips: * There are very few, Tigers (~4) play with respawn timer. (sometimes go back)

steps.description:
* Fly to Crossroads
* Get quest at west, "The Swamp Grows"
* run west until you reach the Bunker
* Turn in + Accept quest The Kolkar of Desolance
* Run back to XR
* Fly to 1K needles

* Accept Family Tree in FreeWind Post! (lvl 32 Req.)
* Move South East to the shimmering flats

* Move to the Raceway
* Accept all quests Expects the 2 from the Dwarf (W / H) 
* Wander around the Shimmering Flats (and Kill / Loot everything!)
steps.tips: * Skip Quests Wharfmaster / Hemet for now

steps.description:
* Turn in All quests, 
* Accept Only:
** Goblin Sponsor,
** Wharfmaster Dizzwig
** Hemet Nesingwary
* Go South to tanaris
* get Flight Point
* Hearthstone to Orgrimmar!
steps.tips: * just Skip the Gnome quests

steps.description:
* Go To bank, Put Kravel's Crate + Kravel's Parts Order in it
* if u have 60 Wools Turn in
* Go to the Valley of Honor, Turn in Quest, Accept next Part
* Go to Cleft of Shadow, Patrol NPC, Accept Alliance Relations
* Go back To the OG WindRider, Fly to Sunrock Retreat
steps.tips: * Learn new Spells

steps.description: * Move Straight to Desolace
* Accept Quest
steps.tips: * Keep on the Road

steps.description:
* Start doing the Tame Quest, only one Kodo at a time can be tamed
* guide them back, TALK TO KODO; Repeat 5 Times
* Go to The Walker Post
* Turn In and Accept ALL QUESTS (SKIP: Magram Alliance, for now)
* Leave Camp, Go East

* Go NorthEast
* kill Kolkar Leader "Kahn", Loot Head
* Go South

* Kill Magram Until you're friendly with Gelkis Fraction!
* Go back to the Camp

* Go East, u can use a shortcut over the Hills (Kodo Skill on the right)
* Turn in / Accept Quest
* move East

* Accept ALL Quests
* get Flight Point
* GO TO IN, make it your new Home!
* Go into the water and gather 10 Shellfish from the Cages
* Give the 10 Shellfish to Jinar'Zillen (BLUE QUESTIONMARK), transform into Bloodbelly fish 
* Swim North ways

* Accept Quest (Little BOOK on a Barrel!)
* Accept Quest From the Agent.
* Go EAST Way

* USE the Crystal (Burning Gem) while targeting Burning Blade NPC (cannel -> dies)
* LOOT EVERY NPC look for Flayed Demon Skin (2% drop chance)
* GO up the Watch Tower MAIN area (Kill Seer), Loot Sceptre
* Enter Main Building, Use the Big Orange Stone in the middle
* Kill Demon (lvl 37), Loot Item
* Leave Area, MAKE SURE you have the Demon Skin!
steps.tips: * Make this quest alone, at least the first 15 NPC (Burning Gem, make this super easy)

steps.description:
* Go back to the Camp
* Turn in Quests / Accept next Parts, 
* Leave Camp Go to the little hut
* accept Quest "Bone Collector"
* Go North East

* Kill Satyr 
* Kill/Loot Shadowstalkers until Shadowstalker Scalp Dropped
* Go back to Ghost Walker Post Turn in Quests / accept next Parts
* Start loot Kodo Bones (Finish it now) (BLUE)
* Move North West.
* Turn in Quest by Agent

* Accept Next Part from Agent
* Kill Nagas (can Drop Golden Key) (G)
* Kill Mobs Loot soft shelled Meat / Loot Silver Key (S)
* if u have both keys! Fight your way North East 
* Go on the Island on the right side hidden in some bushes, there is a chest (QUEST, Turn in)
* go at the end of the Island, There is a Naga Stature, INTERACT, kill mob (lvl 38)
* Return to Agent, Turn in Quests
* Leave East Ways
steps.tips:
* Kill Oracle Until Oracle stone Drops
* there a 2 On the Big Island and 1 on the Small + 1 Underwater

steps.description:
* Go to the Hut in the East, Turn in Quest
* Go to Ghost Walker Post, Turn in Quest (Oracle Stone), Accept new one
* Leave South east way

* Kill Kolkar, Loot Items.
* Loot Meat sacks on the ground near the Tents
* return to Ghost Walker Post
* Turn in Quest Leave West ways to the Gelkis.

* Turn in Quest Accept new "Ongeku"
* Hearthstone back to Shadowprey Village
* Turn in Quests,
* accept new One
* Fly to Thunderbluff, New Skills
* Fly to Camp Taurajo!

* Look for the 3 Quest Items, on the Ground 
* 1. Left side in front of the in, Footprint on the ground.
* 2. on a wood plank , a little badge
* 3. the shield on the wall (chemistry)
* go north into Dustwallow Marsh

* Turn in Quests, Accept new
* TO to Orge, Turn in Quest, Skip next Part (for now)
* behind the Orge, There is a merchant, buy the 3 first aid books!
* get the flight Point
* Fly to Ratchet

* Turn in Quest
* GO TO to bank grab Kavel's items (List / Parts) 
* go to the Docks, turn in quest, accept next part,
* go on the Ship to Booty Bay

* Get first to the Leather Dude, West, Accept quest
* Go to the INN
* Make BootyBay your NEW HOME (BIND)
* Accept All Quests / Turn in
* Get flight Point on top of the INN (right side balcony)
* Fly to Grom'Gol

* Accept All Quests, Excepts (Trollbane, The Vile Reef)
* you should have a full quest log now. 
* Kill Bloodscalp Trolls (B)
* Kill Red Crocodiles (C)
* Kill Elder Tigers (T)
* Kill Raptors (R)
* Complete all Quests
* Go back to Grom'Gol, Turn in 2 Quests Accept only next Parts
steps.tips:
* If Questlog is full, Abort some Quests from Desolace (Elite)
* Necklace quest did not must be complete.

steps.description:
* Kill Trolls, many trolls ....
* Loot heads from HeadHunter
* Loot Necklace from any other troll until complete
* Go to to river in the north, Kill Crocodiles and loot Item (2/2)
* Turn in Quests, Accept next Parts
* Go South on the Little Hill, Kill Sin'Dall (Loot Item)
* Go back to the camp, Turn in "Tiger Mastery"
steps.tips: * Skip Green Hills of STV...

steps.description:
* Go East on the Platform, Kill the foreman (LOOT KEY)
* jump down go to the little House (LOOT BLUEPRINTS), make sure u have room for it
* Kill Geologist, loot crystals
* kill Tiger and Panther (Loot Items)
* Go South to the Orge Camp, Kill Mobs
* Go back to the Camp Turn in Quests (Accept next Panther Part)
* Hearthstone to BootyBay

* Turn In All Quests, 
* Skip Quest Zanzil's Secret + Venture Company Mining
* Accept everything else, (mostly follow parts)
* Fly to Grom'Gol
* Turn in ALL Quests / Accept ONLY Trollbane
* GO On the Zeppelin to UnderCity
steps.tips: * be at least 36

steps.description:
* Go Into UnderCity
* Go to the Bank Put  Fuel Regulator Blueprints and Kravel's Parts in it
* Take Rod of Helcular
* In front of the Flight master (Upper Ring South West) Female UD, Accept 
** To Steal From Thieves
* Fly to Tarrens Mill
steps.tips: * u can lean new Skills here

steps.description:
* Accept ONLY "The Hammer may Fall"
* Fly to Hammerfall

* Accept ALL quests / Turn In
* Make Hammerfall your Home!
* Go east to the monolith, use it, Accept Quest
* Go East

* Leave Hammerfall go to the WaterElementals, 
* In the middle of the Stone Circle Loot the Stone
* Go West, Kill 3 Named Mobs (Near the Barn, In the House, In the Stables)
* go south
steps.tips: * the Farm is a good AOE spot.

steps.description:
* Go South
* Kill Raptors, Loot Hearts 
* Go North West
steps.tips: * If no Raptors available Grind, there are Orge South East.

steps.description:
* Kill Orge (in Cave)
* Kill Syndicate member at the farm (Loot Amulet)
* Go to the Burning elementals, in the Stone circle use Center stone, loot key
* Go South.

* (GROUP QUEST 2+) Kill All Syndicate Member until Sigil of Storm drops (5%)
* go East to the Earth Elementals, Activate Stones, Turn in quest
* Accept new Quest From the Big Stone (Elite)
* HS to Hammerfall

* GO South Kill Trolls for "Call For Arms" (T)
* Go back to hammerfall; Turn in / Accept next part
* GO SOUTHWEST to the Orge (O)
* Go back to Hammerfall / Turn in / Accept next part
steps.tips: * Look for a Giant Roaming in the Area (BLUE)

steps.description:
* ALL Quests in Hammerfall (The Real Thread, The Broken Sigil, Foul Magic + Call For Arms)
* GO SOUTH WEST TO StormGrade; Kill Stormgarde (Loot Sigils)
* Kill Ogre Shaman and Lords (look for Or'Kalar (RED DOT), Loot head)
* Go to the Syndicate Area, Lower Area behind the INN 
* (small passage between WALL and Building), Kill Marez Loot item
* GO back to Hamerfall if done! Turn In ALL Quests / Accept Next Parts / Turn in
* you should be only only one remaining quest Left, Abort it, 
* Fly to Tarrens Mill!
steps.tips:
* THIS STEP IS ONLY IF YOU'RE IN A GRP! 
* otherwise abort ALL Arathi Elite Quests, and skip to next Step (Fly to TM)

steps.description:
* Abort Arathi Quests
* Accept 2 Quests in the Little House (Second Quest has no MARK, talk with NPC)
* Accept Quest in Church (Infiltration)
* Go to the Syndicate Camp (Kill mobs until Quest Item Drops)
* GO North the little Cave, use the Flame of Uzel
* Place the Lion Carcass near the flame, KILL Frostmaw, loot ITEM
* GO West
steps.tips: * KILL ALSO Lions for the Quest Carcass item (Frostmaw)

steps.description:
* Go South, on the GRAVEYARD, the most east GraveStone, use it, turn in Quest. (Ignore NPC)
* Go to TM

* Turn in Quests / Accept, Next parts
* GO north

* Go into The INN (Downstairs kill named, loot Key)
* Upstairs free NPC
* GO West, To Dalaran (Violet Ball)

* Kill Summoner / Kill + Loot Elementals 
* if Finish go Back TO TM

* Turn In Quest, 
* Fly to UC
* Turn IN Quest Direct near the Flight Master,
* GO TO BANK, get every Quest item (Fuel Blueprint + Kravels Parts)
* GO DOWN COOKING AREA (NEAR THE BANK) buy 3 SOOTHING SPICES (for a quest)
* Leave UC go TO OG via Zeppelin!

* Turn in Wool + Silk Quests
* Go north, Turn in Quest
* Go back to OG wind Rider FLY TO CROSSROADS!
* BIND YOURSELF IN CROSSROADS INN
* fly to Freewind Post 1K needles.

* GO to the little outpost before the shimmering flats / Turn in / Accept new quest
* go the Mirage Raceway
* Turn in and accept all NEW QUEST (SKIP ELITE) 4 in total 
* Kill Silithid mobs for the quest + a bonus Quest start drop item
* if finish GO to the little camp in the north, turn in Quest
* Port to Crossroads!
* Turn in Quest (West) / accept next part - after turn in you can destroy Cracked Sili.. item
steps.tips: * you must be at least 90% of lvl 37 if you leave the silithid!

steps.description:
* Turn in FrostMaw Quest / accept Deadmire
* GO to Bank Put in Fizzle Brassbolts' Letter
* Fly to Dustwallow Marsh.
steps.tips: * If u want learn new Skills.

steps.description:
* Accent Quests (SKIP: Overlord, Army, Brood)
* Go south accept quest from Ogre

* Kill Theramore Infiltrators (Theramore Spies) (do not finish!) (RED DOTS)
* grind your way East Kill Spiders (drop acid ), do not finish quest now.

* kill Murlocs, Loot heads
* go south Accept Quest (Soothing Spices) / Turn in Quest / Accept Next part
* Left from the Cabin, is a litte Dirt (grave), interact with it accept quest.

* grind some Raptors
* accept Follow quest, grind mobs while following.
* Kill Spiders / Loot Eyes
* Go south Kill remaining Theramore Skirmisher
* Turn In Quests in Camp 
* Go back accept Orge Quest (Follow ORGE)
* Kill 4 Mobs  
* Go South, Kill all Spiders, finish Acid Quest

* Kill Spiders for Acid (S)
* Finish, Go Turn in Quests

* Turn in quest, (Skip next: crafting sword)
* The DIRT (Grave) next to the Cabin, accept quest.
* Go South

* Go south, Around the Alliance base
* be careful with Guards, on the Docks Dive down
* Look for a Little Box on the Ground (Loot it)
* Die On Purpose and Revine an Graveyard
* Turn in quests / Accept Follow Quest (Stranglethorn)
* Port To CrossRoads
* Fly to Ratchet (Turn in Quest), Go on the Board to Booty bay

* Follow the Docks Accept (The Bloodsail Buccaneers)
* next to the Shark, go in the Cabin (Left), accept Scaring Shaky
* Go in the INN Bind in Booty Bay
* Fly To Grom'Gol

* Accept Mok'thrandin's Enchantments,  The Vile Reef, Bloodscalp Clan Heads
* turn in Quest
* Go back to Grom'Gol
* Turn in / accept next part
steps.tips: * be at least 95% of lvl 38, before returning back!

steps.description:
* Dive on the ground (Inside the wall, a stone panel), be careful 2 elite mobs.
* Go north and Grind your way to the 2 Troll Chiefs, Kill / Loot Heads
* you can grind if you don't have enough money for your lvl 40 mount at this spot
* Go back to Grom'Gol
* Put the Heads in the cooking pot

* Kill Crocodiles, Loot item
* Go East

* Kill Bhag'thera " /tar Bha "
* Go north to the Nesingwary's Expedition
* Turn in Quest, accept Raptor Quest (Raptor Mastery)
* Use Hearthstone, port to Booty Bay

* Leave Booty Bay
* go after the Tunnel, Left
* Kill NPC
* on a Barrel is a Scroll, Use it.
* Go back, East

* Kill Gorillas until 2 Quests are complete,  Aged Gorilla Sinew (has a very low drop rate!)
* Go back to Booty bay, turn in ALL QUESTS,
* Accept ONLY (Return to MacKinley, The Bloodsail Buccaneers (part 1), Excelsior)
* fly to Grom'Gol

* Turn in + Accept next part of Mok'thardin's Enchantment
* go to the Cooking Pot near the Forge, Accept Quest Spirit Bone Necklace
* Bind yourself in Grom'Gol!
steps.tips:
* If you're 40 and have enough money... Buy a mount now. 
* if you're not 40 Go Grind!
* if you did not have enough money for the Mount Grind!
* Venture Co. Geologists are weak and you get easy exp!

steps.description:
* GET "Fizzle Brassbolds LETTER" FROM THE BANK
* From UC Fly to Hammerfall, Arathi Highlands
* RUN the way down until you reach the BadLands
